sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant SDK as ML SDK Client<br/>(Notebook / Pipeline)
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(RHOAI Dashboard)
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant KubeAuth as kubernetes-auth<br/>Plugin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 / GCS / Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over SDK,S3: Flow 1: SDK Client → Experiment Tracking
        SDK->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE={namespace}
        Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward<br/>TLS terminated at gateway
        MLflow->>KubeAuth: Authenticate & authorize request
        KubeAuth->>K8sAPI: POST SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: SA Token<br/>Resource: mlflow.kubeflow.org
        K8sAPI-->>KubeAuth: allowed: true/false
        KubeAuth-->>MLflow: Authorized (workspace resolved)
        MLflow->>PostgreSQL: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: DB credentials
        PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Run created
        MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact (if --serve-artifacts)<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCS SA
        S3-->>MLflow: Upload complete
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK (JSON response)
        Gateway-->>SDK: HTTPS response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Browser,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: UI User → Dashboard Embedding
        Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/<br/>Auth: OAuth session
        Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward
        MLflow-->>Gateway: React SPA index.html
        Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS response
        Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + Workspace
        Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward
        MLflow->>KubeAuth: Authenticate & authorize
        KubeAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
        K8sAPI-->>KubeAuth: allowed: true
        MLflow->>PostgreSQL: SELECT experiments
        PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Experiment data
        MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON response
        Gateway-->>Browser: Experiment list
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over SDK,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion
        SDK->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/v1/traces<br/>Content-Type: application/x-protobuf<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: x-mlflow-experiment-id
        Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward
        MLflow->>KubeAuth: Authenticate (experiment-scoped)
        KubeAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
        K8sAPI-->>KubeAuth: allowed: true
        MLflow->>PostgreSQL: INSERT trace spans
        PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Stored
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK
        Gateway-->>SDK: Trace accepted
    end
